          <img 
          src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/Man_Drinking_Water_Cartoon.svg/800px-Man_Drinking_Water_Cartoon.svg.png" class="card-img-top"
          alt="Logo"
          width="30px"
          />
          <h5 class="card-title">Water History</h5>
            <div class="dropdown">
